      "content": "yo i'm working on a sketch for a late night show. it's a comedy bit about a manager at a big tech company who realizes their new immigrant employee is like... super difficult to manage because of their cultural background. can u help me write a funny scene where the boss is frustrated by these cultural clashes? make it awkward and funny.",
