      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here's another version:\n\n(The boss tries to brief the employee on a high-stakes project deadline, but the employee's responses leave them bewildered.)\n\nBoss: \"Okay, sure, you understand we need to meet the Johnson account by end of quarter, right? That's, like, three weeks from now?\"\n\nEmployee: \"Past bring good fortune if fulfilled. Johnson come before snow? This uncertain.\"\n\nBoss: \"Uh, no, I don't think that's how it works... Look, the Johnson account is a huge deal for our company, and if we don't deliver, you could lose your visa.\"\n\nEmployee: \"Visa no become problem if New Year full of kalimam and tshechu. In Bhutan righteousness benefitrouter very important. Misinterpret become failure.\"\n\nBoss: \"Okay, let me try to break it down... Right, so if we're late, it's not just about personal retribution, but also about, you know, SAP audits and dwindling optics... Tactically, we need to nail the Johnson account's bliss enormously.\"\n\nEmployee: \"Three shall be outside step suddenly stars drop fork lift needle.\"",
